{"word":"G2045 - ἐρευνάω - ereunáō - er-yoo-nah'-o - Search","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐρευνάω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ereunáō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">er-yoo-nah'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Search</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - ஆராய்"},{"paragraph":"to search, examine into: absolutely"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Apparently from <a href=\"#/G2046 - ἐρέω - eréō - er-eh'-o/2046\">G2046</a> (through the idea of <i>inquiry</i>); to <i>seek</i>, that is, (figuratively) to <i>investigate:</i> - search.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1830/1830\">G1830</a>, <a href=\"#/G2045/2045\">G2045</a>"}]}